should be modified to something like:

JavaSource source = JavaSource.create(...);
try {
source.runUserActionTask(new Task&amp;lt;CompilationController&amp;gt;() {
public void run(CompilationController cc) throws Exception {
cc.toPhase(JavaSource.Phase.RESOLVED);
Element element = handle.resolveElement(cc);
...
}
}, true);
} catch (IOException ex) {}*`|`*

